# --- Eval artifacts ---
# NOTE: eval results are intentionally version-controlled (ARCHITECTURE §7.2) — they are
# the durable, Langfuse-independent record of each run. So they are NOT ignored here.
# If you ever want to stop tracking them, uncomment:
#   evals/results/*.json
#   evals/results/*.csv
#   !evals/results/.gitkeep

